The ASK meta-brand public landing site — a reference implementation of the
ASK design family.

This product vendors foundations from design-system-ASK
(github.com/apexSolarKiss/design-system-ASK):
  - colors_and_type.css        — canonical tokens (Tier 1 + Tier 2)
  - fonts/                      — Inter + JetBrains Mono variable webfonts (OFL; see fonts/*-OFL.txt)
  - assets/logo-ASK.*          — the logo-ASK wordmark (ASK Tier 3)

When this site and design-system-ASK disagree on a foundation value, the
canonical design-system-ASK file (itself downstream of ASK's
visual-identity-system.md) wins. This site adds layout only; it defines no
new tokens.

